OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772358841
OL,3,CWhy Iran is attacking US bases in the
OL,4,CGulf rather than focusing on Israel
OL,6,FSo far the unprecedented aspect about
OL,7,Fthis, the third Gulf War, is the
OL,8,FIranian targeting of several US bases
OL,9,Fin the Gulf. We've seen big plumes of
OL,10,Fsmoke blossom as Iranian missiles slam
OL,11,Finto near neighbours like Bahrain and
OL,12,FAbu Dhabi.
OL,14,FHere in Tel Aviv the air raid sirens
OL,15,Fhave been frequent but the missile
OL,16,Fsalvoes smaller than those sent this
OL,17,Fway last June. They have come in by
OL,18,Fthe dozen rather than hundreds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
