OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772358841
OL,3,CWhy Iran is attacking US bases in the
OL,4,CGulf rather than focusing on Israel
OL,6,FThe Israeli/US umbrella of interceptor
OL,7,Fmissiles defending this country is
OL,8,Funrivalled. During June's 12-day war
OL,9,Fthey shot down 85% of the Iranian
OL,10,Fballistic missiles that they tried to
OL,11,Fintercept.
OL,13,FOf course Iran could be holding back a
OL,14,Fmore potent threat. Or they may have
OL,15,Fmade the strategic decision to focus
OL,16,Fon the Americans more than the
OL,17,FIsraelis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
