OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772358841
OL,3,CWhy Iran is attacking US bases in the
OL,4,CGulf rather than focusing on Israel
OL,6,FFrom their point of view why strike
OL,7,FLittle Satan when the Great Satan is
OL,8,Fcloser by and perhaps more poorly
OL,9,Fdefended? The Gulf targets may provide
OL,10,Fmore bang for their buck.
OL,12,FThe Iranians know that their ultimate
OL,13,Fcurrency in this war is dead Americans.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
