OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772358841
OL,3,CWhy Iran is attacking US bases in the
OL,4,CGulf rather than focusing on Israel
OL,6,FWhatever damage Iran is able to
OL,7,Finflict abroad, it's undoubtedly far
OL,8,Fless than the damage being sustained
OL,9,Fat home.
OL,11,FLast June, the Israelis paved the way
OL,12,Ffor American B2 bombers to attack
OL,13,Fthree nuclear sites unchallenged.
OL,15,FThe Iranian air defence system was
OL,16,Fbeaten to such an extent that in the
OL,17,Fend Israeli jets were flying over
OL,18,FTehran in broad daylight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
