OL,3,CWhy Iran is attacking US bases in the
OL,4,CGulf rather than focusing on Israel
OL,6,FBut while Iran is struggling to defend
OL,7,Fitself, it can still retaliate.
OL,8,FAmerican fatalities will test
OL,9,FPresident Trump's resolve.
OL,11,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,12,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,13,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,14,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
